class=\"toc-text\">原理</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">可以参考</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A3%85%E5%A4%87%E9%81%AE%E7%BD%A9%EF%BC%88camera-overlay%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E7%82%B9%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">装备遮罩（camera_overlay）的一点研究</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#by-CR-019\"><span class=\"toc-text\">by CR_019</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">指令</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">播放</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">开始播放</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%88%E6%AD%A2%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">终止播放</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9A%82%E5%81%9C%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">暂停播放</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">继续播放</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">删除单个玩家的播放设置</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">删除所有玩家的播放设置</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%BA%8F%E5%88%97%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">关于序列图片</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E5%BA%8F%E5%88%97%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">如何导出序列图片</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">推荐尺寸</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">注意事项</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"洛风澜_Sea","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud-photo.windwaves.top/author.png","link":"/","description":"欢迎大家来看我的博客，希望里面的内容对你有帮助!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/WindWavesSea","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/icon/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/3493092078389380"},"twich":{"icon":"/svg/icon/twich.svg","link":"https://www.twitch.tv/windwaves_sea"},"youtube":{"icon":"/svg/icon/youtube.svg","link":"https://www.youtube.com/@WindWaves_Sea"}}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{}}